<div type="letter">
<pb facs="1361418" n="1"/>
<opener>
<lb/><abbr>Illustriss.<hi rend="sup">o</hi></abbr> et <abbr>Celeber.<hi rend="sup">o</hi></abbr> Viro <rs key="pers_DE-588-119166895" type="person">Nicolao Bernoulli</rs>
<lb/><abbr>S. P. D.</abbr> <rs key="pers_DE-588-102552517" type="person">Petrus Antonius Michelotti</rs>
</opener>
<p>
<lb/>Quin meas <rs key="B_1718-04-22_991170517055705501" type="letter">literas</rs> ante decem dies istuc missas un<choice><orig><g ref="#ahat">창</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice>
   <lb/>cum <rs key="B_1718-04-09_991170515152605501" type="letter">iis</rs> (quas<del> a</del> <abbr>Celeber.</abbr> <rs key="pers_DE-588-118509969" type="person">Patruus</rs><note type="editorial">Bernoulli, Johann (1667-1748)</note> Tuus ad me trans<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>misit) acceperis, Vir <abbr>Clariss.<hi rend="sup">e</hi></abbr>, nullus dubitandi mi<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>hi relinquitur locus. Libenter tamen resciam an
               <lb/>revera easdemmet literas omnes<note type="editorial">Im Brief von Johann I Bernoulli an Nicolaus I Bernoulli von 1718.04.09 wird auch ein Briefwechsel von Nicolaus I mit seinem Bruder Benedict Bernoulli erw채hnt. Dieser scheint aber nicht erhalten zu sein. Deshalb kann nicht verifiziert werden, ob alle Briefe, literas omnes, nur die beiden oben genannten oder noch weitere, nicht ermittelbare Briefe umfasst.</note> acceptaris. In
               <lb/>una ex tuis <rs key="B_1718-03-19_991170517055905501" type="letter">epistolis</rs> dixisti quod pressio fluidi per<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>pendiculariter superficiem quamlibet continen<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tem prementis est <add>in unoquoque puncto</add> proportionalis altitudini
               <lb/>verticali fluidi supra hoc punctum, atque ista
               <lb/>altitudo quo singulis sectionis horizontalis punctis
               <lb/>eadem. Peto a Te huius <abbr>proposi.<hi rend="sup">is</hi></abbr> demonstratio<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>nem, quam ex Hydrostaticis p<unclear>a</unclear>tere indicasti. Spe<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>ro quod <abbr>Excell.<hi rend="sup">um</hi></abbr> <abbr>Proc.<hi rend="sup">rem</hi></abbr> <rs key="pers_DE-588-121843858" type="person">Theupol<choice><orig><g ref="#um">큰</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice></rs><note type="editorial">Tiepolo, Lorenzo (1673-1742)</note> non semel
               <lb/>salutaveris.
            </p>
<closer>Tu interim vale, et mihi impera.
               <lb/><dateline/>Dabam <rs key="place_GEO-3164603" type="place">Venetiis</rs> <date when="1718-05-02"><choice><abbr>a. d.</abbr><expan>ad diem</expan></choice> 2 Maii 1718</date>.<note hand="pers_DE-588-119166895"><foreign xml:lang="ger"><abbr>Empf.</abbr> den <date when="1718-05-03">3<hi rend="sup">ten</hi></date>.</foreign></note>
</closer>
